    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.2",
      "en": "Elemento introduces a sovereign control and federation layer above public clouds, private clouds, sovereign providers, hypervisors and native AtomOS infrastructure.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.20",
      "en": "Hypervisor Fabric",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.21",
      "en": "Elemento discovers existing infrastructure, normalises capabilities through C4, exposes them through Electros and allows teams to govern, broker, orchestrate and optimise resources through one operational model.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.22",
      "en": "Connect existing infrastructures, clouds and services without replacement.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.23",
      "en": "Introduce visibility, governance, policy enforcement and federation controls.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.24",
      "en": "Enable workload mobility, brokerage, sovereignty policies and intelligent placement.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.25",
      "en": "Deploy the Metacloud your way — centralised, customer-hosted or federated.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.26",
      "en": "A shared Elemento environment operated as a common governance layer. Fastest time to value with Elemento-operated Electros.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.27",
      "en": "Elemento deployed within the customer's own environment. Maximum sovereignty and compliance by design.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.28",
      "en": "Multiple providers participating within a common federation while preserving operational independence.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.29",
      "en": "Book a Metacloud Assessment to map your estate and identify the fastest path to sovereign control.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.3",
      "en": "Elemento is a Metacloud platform. Rather than replacing existing infrastructure, Elemento introduces a control and federation layer above private clouds, public clouds, sovereign clouds, hypervisors and Kubernetes environments.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.4",
      "en": "The platform enables organisations to discover, govern, broker and orchestrate resources across heterogeneous providers through a unified operational model.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.5",
      "en": "Governance is decoupled from infrastructure ownership. Elemento federates what exists — it does not replace it.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.6",
      "en": "Retain ownership of workloads and data while governing across providers.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.7",
      "en": "No dependency on a single cloud, hypervisor or sovereign provider.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.8",
      "en": "Sovereignty becomes a workload policy, not a provider decision.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "body.platform.p.9",
      "en": "Move and broker workloads without application re-architecture.",
      "it": "",
      "fr": "",
      "source": "platform.html",
      "context": "<p>"
    },
